-- 6,10,15,5,12,4,13,7,2,14 -- k(k+1)/2 (mod 2^n) -- A329278 Irregular table read by rows. The n-th row is the permutation of {0, 1, 2, ..., 2^n-1} given by T(n,k) = k(k+1)/2 (mod 2^n).
